      "content": "but the fight feels so exhausting. like, if they keep clinging to these bits of data and memories that are just gonna vanish eventually, aren't they just prolonging the suffering? i'm wondering if the character would actually find more relief in just... letting go early? instead of waiting for the slow, painful deletion?",
