      "content": "it just feels like there's no real difference between fighting to stay and just giving up, you know? if the end is inevitable, then why does it even matter if they choose it themselves or wait for the system to do it? it's like... if they just ended it on their own terms, it wouldn't even be a tragedy, it would just be... final. like, wouldn't that be more peaceful for them?",
